rnal rest — Shina Oludare  (@sportingshina) January 21, 2021  More details to follow Vanguard News Nigeria Former national team keeper and assistant coach of the Super Eagles, Joe Erico has tipped FIFA Under-17 World Cup star, Dele Alampasu to be the next Super Eagles keeper whenever high flying Vincent Enyeama made his exits. November 17, 2013 In "Sports" After joining the call for Keshi’s departure as Super Eagles Head Coach, former assistant Coach of the Super Eagles, Joe Erico has said it was only natural that Keshi called it quits after the failure to qualify Nigeria for the 2015 Afcon. December 24, 2014 In "Sports" Joe Erico, a retired goalkeeper of the former Green Eagles in the 1970s, wants total support for the Super Eagles’ Coach, Stephen Keshi, in the October13 clash against the Lone Star of Liberia in Calabar. September 30, 2012 In "Sports"